metadata.name: Boredo Prime
metadata.description:
An open edition of a photograph of BAYC #7073 spray painted into the bottom of an Amazon Prime labelled shipping box ("UNTITLED"). 

Through a raffle process, at time of a future snapshot, one of the wallets collected (in said snapshot) will be randomly selected to receive the original artwork, at no personal cost to them. Because the artwork is on a shipping box, I will mail the winner the box. I'll put a few fun prizes and surprises in the box, too. 

It'll be a sincere care package.  

I've got a kind of over/under utility in mind for this edition. 

If it's "under," then I'll do something like: make the tokens burnable for an original artwork or something else if you could care less about the original.

If it's "over," then I'll do some real combination-style redemption opportunities, because it'll be "game on." (C'esi n'est pas une game)

Thx  
-MP
